#: apps/orders/models.py:230
msgid ""
"You already have an active order. Please wait for it to be completed or "
"cancel it before placing a new one."
msgstr ""
"Ya tiene un pedido activo. Espere a que se complete o cancélelo antes de "
"hacer uno nuevo."

#: apps/orders/models.py:261
#, python-format
